snippet.title: Tarek Fatah making fun of Pakistan by calling "Pappu" for its coward army after surgical strike

localized.description:
In the news channel debate ,Tarek Fatah slams Pakistan by calling "Pappu" for its coward pak army after surgical strike by Indian army

Sending a clear message to Pakistan in the wake of the Uri attack, India said on Thursday it carried out surgical strikes on terrorist launch pads across the Line of Control on Wednesday night, inflicting heavy casualties.
